data.description: BACK ON THE MARKET AT NO FAULT OF THE SELLER! 4 bedroom 3 bathroom home in the highly sought after neighborhood of Forest Hills! Downstairs you'll find an open floor plan with a formal dining room, kitchen, eating area, and living room. Additionally, right off the living room there is a bedroom/guest room and full bathroom. Upstairs is the spacious master bedroom/bathroom, 2 additional bedrooms, a full bathroom, laundry room, and a large bonus room that would be perfect for an office space, playroom, or guest room. The fenced in backyard has a covered patio and plenty of trees for privacy.
